ZH: 轮流来分享你的经验。
EN: Take turns to share your experience.

ZH: 我们可以轮流扫地。
EN: We can take turns to sweep the floor.

ZH: 他们轮流唱歌。
EN: They take turns to sing.

ZH: 请你们轮流回答问题。
EN: Please take turns to answer the questions.

ZH: 他们轮流担任班长。
EN: They take turns to be the class monitor.

ZH: 我们轮流洗碗。
EN: We take turns to wash the dishes.

ZH: 他们轮流上场比赛。
EN: They take turns to play in the game.

ZH: 老师让我们轮流写作文。
EN: The teacher asked us to take turns writing essays.

ZH: 我们轮流组队做项目。
EN: We take turns to form teams for the project.

ZH: 轮流做饭的话你得等一会儿。
EN: You have to wait for a while if we take turns cooking.

ZH: 他们轮流护送犯人。
EN: They take turns escorting prisoners.

ZH: 我们轮流照看婴儿。
EN: We take turns to take care of the baby.

ZH: 姐妹俩轮流使用这台电脑。
EN: The two sisters take turns using this computer.

ZH: 轮流做家务可以减轻负担。
EN: Taking turns to do housework can lighten the burden.

ZH: 我们轮流参观各个景点。
EN: We take turns to visit various attractions.

ZH: 他们轮流讲故事。
EN: They take turns telling stories.

ZH: 老师让我们轮流做演讲。
EN: The teacher asked us to take turns giving speeches.

ZH: 轮流安排工作可以提高工作效率。
EN: Rotating work assignments can improve work efficiency.

ZH: 今天你下午开会，明天我轮流去。
EN: You have a meeting this afternoon, and I will attend it tomorrow in a rotation.

ZH: 轮流操作电脑可以提高技术水平。
EN: Taking turns operating the computer can improve technical skills.
